    <h2>Bulb </h2>
    <p> Click the bulb below to turn it ON or OFF.</p>

    <img id="bulb" src="https://www.w3schools.com/js/pic_bulboff.gif" alt="Bulb">

    <p id="status">The bulb is currently OFF.</p>
    <script src="tasks.js"></script>

